summary: An Ordinance transferring the sum of Sixty-three and 87/100 ($63.87) Dollars from Local Improvement District No. 1773 Fund, into the General Fund of the City of Seattle, for the purpose of reimbursing said General Fund, for the deficiency in the Fixed Estimate of said district, for the improvement of West Sixty-first Street, et al, by constructing sewers therein, as provided for in Ordinance No. 18672.
